{"tid":1693280,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［警世］我屌哂你地老母，唔好再講「兄弟爬山，各自努力」","createTime":"2019-11-04T13:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T11:44:37.000Z","uid":294,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1b01d02db3b23e46ad9a9ad397e39f7fdb169496","tid":1693280,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「<span style=\"color: red;\">一齊</span>爬山，<span style=\"color: red;\">一齊</span>努力」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1。摺完紙唔係返屋企睇Live 然後話唔割又心痛，麻煩有事都要行出黎（可以衡量企幾前，但一定要帶野出黎）。<br />\n2。勇武完都唔係休息唔係屌人淨係唱歌摺紙，你除左個豬咀一樣可以唱歌摺紙。<br />\n<br />\n全民一齊和一齊勇<br />\n<br />\n由今日開始<br />\n「一齊爬山，一齊努力」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4204362c1a1d870072aaa4043804b85e624880","tid":1693280,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:43:14.000Z","msg":"「一齊爬山，一齊努力」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5894a0ae974d1c5c7c8b0c2026ae7c7bcd4e3c2","tid":1693280,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:43:55.000Z","msg":"「一齊爬山，一齊努力」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa93fca584e6417902ff959a74d2cde9d195614e","tid":1693280,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:45:01.000Z","msg":"「一齊爬山，一齊努力」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33